sky.mix.uk.title: Qatar F1 GP Highlights
sky.mix.uk.description: It's lights out in Qatar. As Lando Norris lines up in P2 a win away from the world championship, it's down to polesitter Oscar Piastri and Max Verstappen to deny the Brit the title. (30.11)

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest Games: B'ming/A.Villa
sky.mix.uk.description: A classic Premier League clash between Birmingham and Aston Villa in 2002. There was an intense atmosphere at St Andrew's with just a single point separating the bitter rivals.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest: WBA v Man Utd 2013
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive a classic Premier League match. Here, West Bromwich Albion take on Man Utd back in 2013 in a ten-goal thriller in what was Sir Alex Ferguson's final game in charge.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest: Cardiff v Liverpool
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive a classic Premier League match. Here, Cardiff City take on Liverpool at the Cardiff City Stadium back in 2014, in a match that saw nine goals and a Luis Suarez hat-trick.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest: L'pool/Arsenal 09
sky.mix.uk.description: Remember a classic match from the Premier League. Here, Liverpool and Arsenal play out an absolute thriller at Anfield that saw Arsenal striker Andrey Arshavin steal the show.

sky.mix.uk.title: The Rise Of MVG (2013)
sky.mix.uk.description: Debuting in 2008 and bursting onto the scene in 2013 where he took the great Phil Taylor all the way, hear first-hand accounts of Michael Van Gerwen's incredible rise. Ep 5.

sky.mix.uk.title: Gary Anderson: Back2Back Champion
sky.mix.uk.description: Gary Anderson tells the story of his PDC World Darts Championship triumphs in 2015 and 2016, as the Scotsman become only the third player to win back-to-back titles. Ep 6.

sky.mix.uk.title: Rob Cross: A Year To Remember 2018
sky.mix.uk.description: At the first time of asking, Rob Cross shocked the world on his PDC World Darts Championship debut by defeating the retiring Phil Taylor in the final at Alexandra Palace in 2018. Ep 7.

sky.mix.uk.title: Peter Wright: Double Champ 20 & 22
sky.mix.uk.description: A two-time winner of the coveted Sid Waddell Trophy, Peter 'Snakebite' Wright recounts the highs and lows of PDC World Darts Championship glory. Ep 8.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 12/13: Watford v Leicester
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive a classic clash from the English Football League. Here, Watford meet Leicester City in the famous second leg of their Championship play-off semi-final in May 2013.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 13/14: Sheff Weds v Leeds Utd
sky.mix.uk.description: Relive a classic match from the Football League. Here, Yorkshire rivals Sheffield Wednesday and Leeds United meet at Hillsborough in January 2014 in a memorable game for the Owls.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 13/14: Derby County v N.Forest
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive a classic clash from the English Football League. Here, Derby County meet Nottingham Forest in the Sky Bet Championship.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 13/14: QPR v N. Forest
sky.mix.uk.description: Relive a classic match from the English Football League. Here, QPR host Nottingham Forest at Loftus Road in the 2013-14 season in a seven-goal thriller.

sky.mix.uk.title: Hero World Challenge 2016 Hlts
sky.mix.uk.description: Action from the Hero World Challenge on the PGA Tour from the Bahamas. Last year, Bubba Watson seized the title by a three-stroke margin ahead of compatriot Patrick Reed.

sky.mix.uk.title: Golf Academy: S Lyle Full Swing
sky.mix.uk.description: Two-time Major champion and Hall of Famer Sandy Lyle gives you his tips for success on the course. This lesson is dedicated to achieving a perfect swing.

sky.mix.uk.title: Golf Academy
sky.mix.uk.description: Some of golf's top professionals share their tips and advice for improving your game, from new starters to scratch golfers. Here, superstar Rory McIlroy is on hand with some advice. Part 1.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 14/15: Brentford v Fulham
sky.mix.uk.description: Relive some classic action from the English Football League. Here, a west London derby in the Sky Bet Championship between Brentford and Fulham at Griffin Park in November 2014.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 14/15: Derby County v N.Forest
sky.mix.uk.description: Relive some classic English Football League action. Here, a Midlands derby in the Sky Bet Championship between Derby County and Nottingham Forest at the iPro Stadium in January 2015.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 14/15: Norwich v Ipswich
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive some classic action from the EFL. Here, Norwich City and Ipswich Town clash in an East Anglian derby at Carrow Road back in March 2015.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 14/15: Wolves v Leeds Utd
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive some classic action from the EFL. Here, Wolverhampton Wanderers host Leeds United at Molineux in April 2015 in a thrilling game that saw seven goals.

sky.mix.uk.title: WBBL Perth S v Melbourne R Hlts
sky.mix.uk.description: Perth Scorchers take on the reigning champions Melbourne Renegades - who are well off the form that took them to last season's title. Both teams are locked on eight points. (02.12)

sky.mix.uk.title: Ladies European Tour Golf Hlts
sky.mix.uk.description: Tournament highlights from the Andalucia Costa Del Sol Open de Espana, the climactic event of the Ladies European Tour season taking place at Real Guadalhorce Club de Golf.

sky.mix.uk.description: Luke Robinson's Huddersfield Giants play host to Leigh Leopards in the Betfred Super League. Leigh's play-off hopes were dealt a blow last week in defeat to the Black and Whites.

sky.mix.uk.title: NFL Buccaneers @ Rams Highlights
sky.mix.uk.description: Bitesize highlights as the 8-2 Los Angeles Rams, riding a five-game winning streak in their bid to win the NFC West, welcome Todd Bowles' 6-4 Tampa Bay Buccaneers. (23.11)

sky.mix.uk.title: NBA: Thunder @ Warriors
sky.mix.uk.description: The Oklahoma City Thunder, the reigning NBA champions, hit the road for a regular-season clash with the Golden State Warriors. The 20-1 Thunder registered a 12th straight win last time out.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest Games:Arsenal/Spurs 08
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive a classic match from the Premier League. Here, Arsenal meet Tottenham Hotspur in the north London derby in 2008-09 season, in a match that saw a stunning comeback.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest: Man U/Arsenal '98
sky.mix.uk.description: Remember a classic match from the Premier League. Here, Arsenal visit Alex Ferguson's Manchester United at Old Trafford back in the 1997-98 season.

sky.mix.uk.description: Argentina battle New Zealand during round two of the 2025 Rugby Championship. The All Blacks returned to the top of the world rankings with their win over Los Pumas in Cordoba.

sky.mix.uk.title: WBBL Perth S v Melbourne R Hlts
sky.mix.uk.description: Perth Scorchers take on the reigning champions Melbourne Renegades - who are well off the form that took them to last season's title. Both teams are locked on eight points. (02.12)

sky.mix.uk.title: Wade v Thornton: Wld Grand Prix 14
sky.mix.uk.description: Revisit an incredible match at the 2014 World Grand Prix of Darts, as James Wade and Robert Thornton both hit nine-darters during their round two meeting. Contains flashing images.

sky.mix.uk.title: Live Mosconi Cup Pool
sky.mix.uk.description: The race for the prestigious Mosconi Cup gets underway with the opening day of nine-ball action between Team Europe and Team USA. Team Europe eye a sixth consecutive title on home soil.

sky.mix.uk.title: Ladies European Tour Golf Hlts
sky.mix.uk.description: Tournament highlights from the Andalucia Costa Del Sol Open de Espana, the climactic event of the Ladies European Tour season taking place at Real Guadalhorce Club de Golf.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest: Man Utd/Everton 2012
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive a classic match from the Premier League. Here, Man Utd host Everton at Old Trafford in a captivating eight-goal thriller back in 2012.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest Games:Newc/Leics '97
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive a classic Premier League match. Here, Newcastle United host Leicester City in a seven-goal thriller at St James' Park in the 1996-97 season.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest Games:L'Pool/Man U '94
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive a Premier League classic. Here, arch rivals Liverpool and Manchester United meet at Anfield back in 1994 in a match that saw one of the Premier League's great comebacks.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest: Swansea/C Palace '16
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive a classic Premier League match. Here, Swansea City take on Crystal Palace at the Liberty Stadium in a high-scoring encounter in the 2016-17 season.

sky.mix.uk.title: Gerwyn Price: Welsh Glory 2021
sky.mix.uk.description: Hear Gerwyn Price as he recounts the emotions and near misses of the 2021 PDC World Darts Championship. Ep 9.

sky.mix.uk.title: The Greatest Leg - 2023 Final
sky.mix.uk.description: In 2023, both MVG and Michael Smith were on course to record a nine-dart leg; the Dutchman fell short by a single dart, but the Englishman achieved perfection. Ep 10.

sky.mix.uk.title: 30 Years of the PDC World Champs'
sky.mix.uk.description: In celebration of 30 years of the PDC World Darts Championship, take a look back at the very first tournament, a classic final from 2007 and one of the greatest legs ever played. Ep 1.

sky.mix.uk.title: The Taylor Years
sky.mix.uk.description: Hear from the legendary Phil Taylor as the 16-time world champion recounts his glory years at the PDC World Darts Championship. Ep 2.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 14/15: Swindon v Sheff Utd
sky.mix.uk.description: Relive a classic match from the English Football League. Here, Swindon Town host Sheffield United at the County Ground in a 10-goal thriller in the play-offs back in May 2015.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 14/15: Norwich v Ipswich
sky.mix.uk.description: Relive some classic action from the English Football League. Here, East Anglian rivals Norwich City and Ipswich Town meet at Carrow Road in the Sky Bet play-offs in May 2015.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 14/15: Derby County v Leeds

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 15/16: Hull City v Reading
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive some classic action from the EFL. Here, Hull City take on Reading at the KC Stadium in December 2015 in a thrilling clash that saw a late winner.

sky.mix.uk.title: PGA Tour Golf Highlights
sky.mix.uk.description: Tournament highlights from RSM Classic, a PGA Tour event held at Sea Island Golf Club. Maverick McNealy collected his first tour win here in his 142nd start a year.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 15/16: QPR v Middlesbrough
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive some classic action from the English Football League. Here, QPR host Middlesbrough in a five-goal thriller at Loftus Road in the 2015-16 season.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 15/16: B'ham v Middlesbrough
sky.mix.uk.description: Relive some classic action from the English Football League. Here, Birmingham City take on Middlesbrough at St Andrew's in a four-goal thriller in the 2015-16 season.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 15/16:Middlesbrough v Brighton
sky.mix.uk.description: A look back at some classic matches from the English Football League. Here, Middlesbrough take on Brighton and Hove Albion in a tense Championship promotion decider in May 2016.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 16/17: Aston Villa v N. Forest
sky.mix.uk.description: A look back at some classic matches from the English Football League. Here, Aston Villa play Nottingham Forest in a thrilling draw in September 2016 in the Sky Bet Championship.

sky.mix.uk.title: WBBL Melbourne S v Sydney S Hlts
sky.mix.uk.description: Two games remain for the Melbourne Stars, whose winning run came to an end against WBBL pacesetters Hobart, as Elyse Villani and co take on Ellyse Perry's Sydney Sixers. (02.12)

sky.mix.uk.title: WBBL Sydney T v Brisbane H Hlts
sky.mix.uk.description: With qualification hopes all but over, Phoebe Litchfield and the Sydney Thunder take on bottom side Brisbane Heat - who are still without a WBBL win to their name this campaign. (02.12)

sky.mix.uk.description: Table toppers Hull KR play host to St Helens in the Betfred Super League. Last week, the Robins gained the psychological edge over Warrington ahead of their Wembley Challenge Cup meeting.

sky.mix.uk.title: Abu Dhabi F1 GP Highlights 2023
sky.mix.uk.description: For the final time this year, Formula 1 goes racing as Yas Marina Circuit stages the Abu Dhabi Grand Prix. Will Max Verstappen bookend a record-breaking season with a 19th race win? (26.11)

sky.mix.uk.title: Abu Dhabi F1 GP Highlights 2024
sky.mix.uk.description: In what is Lewis Hamilton's final Mercedes race, it's Lando Norris and Oscar Piastri who lock out the front row in a bid to secure McLaren a first constructors' title since 1998. (08.12)

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest Games:Charlton/WHU '01
sky.mix.uk.description: Relive one of the Premier League's great games. Here, Charlton Athletic take on West Ham United at The Valley in November 2001 in a pulsating encounter that went down to the wire.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest: Man City/Man Utd 2002
sky.mix.uk.description: Relive one of the Premier League's great games. Here, Manchester City take on Manchester United back in 2002 in the last Manchester derby to be played at Maine Road.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest : Watford/Fulham 2006
sky.mix.uk.description: A chance to relive a classic Premier League match. Here, Watford meet Fulham at Vicarage Road in October 2006 in a remarkable match that had a dramatic late finish.

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest:Liverpool/Chelsea 2001
sky.mix.uk.description: Relive a classic Premier League match. Here, Liverpool play host to Chelsea at Anfield in the 2000-2001 season, with both sides battling for places in Europe near the season's end.

sky.mix.uk.title: The Rugby Championships 2025

E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip featuring animals and food, from the always hilarious Tube that is Rude.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Giuseppi's: Gordon Ramsay visits a family-owned Italian in Michigan, run by a father and son who constantly clash. Can he get the restaurant - and the family - back on track? (S2 Ep1) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Stop Arguing and Start Thanking: When Beverly invites Murray's unreliable brother Marvin to visit at Thanksgiving, she reignites their long-standing feud. (S1 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Shopping: Erica's new job at a department store is put in jeopardy when Beverly takes advantage of her daughter's employee discount far too frequently. (S1 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: E My Sports: When Bart starts earning money from video game competitions, Homer becomes his coach, and their team make it to the finals in South Korea. (S30 Ep17/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bart vs. Itchy & Scratchy: Bart's upset about a new, all-girl Itchy and Scratchy. Then he joins an all-girl pranking crew, Bossy Riot. (S30 Ep18/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Romance Recalibration: Penny thinks that Leonard has stopped making an effort in their relationship, so she decides to go away for a spa weekend with Amy. (S10 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Emotion Detection Automation: Sheldon tests a new invention after hearing that it could help him to read people's emotions. Raj seeks dating advice. (S10 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Fight or Flight: After a reunion weekend with Phil's old buddies, Claire jumps at the chance to snag the only first-class seat left on the flight home, leaving Phil in coach. (S6 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Connection Lost: Claire's computer becomes the hub of all the family's activities when she gets stuck at the airport and is desperate to reach Haley after a big fight. (S6 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Irish Pub Formulation: A visit from Raj's sister Priya creates tension among the guys, especially when Leonard asks Sheldon to conceal his romantic past with her. (S4 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Apology Insufficiency: Leonard thinks his dating problems are due to a lack of confidence, and vows to be self-assured around attractive women. Howard is called by the FBI. (S4 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The 21-Second Excitation: The gang's plans to attend a film screening are scuppered by Sheldon's nemesis Wil Wheaton. Penny and Bernadette invite Amy to her first slumber party. (S4 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Boyfriend Complexity: When Penny's father visits, Leonard discovers that her parents still think that he and Penny are a couple, so he takes advantage of the situation. (S4 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: Carbon Dating and a Stuffed Raccoon: Sheldon gets into trouble with fellow child genius Paige at the Science Museum. Meemaw has a jumble sale in her garage. (S2 Ep7/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: An 8-Bit Princess and a Flat Tire Genius: Meemaw gives Sheldon his first video game. George Sr gets jealous when Georgie bonds with Herschel from the garage. (S2 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Daughter Also Rises: Lisa meets an intellectual romantic who shares her passion for culture. (S23 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: At Long Last Leave: The Simpsons are evicted from Springfield and join an off-grid community, but Marge and Homer meet hostility when they try to sneak back into town. (S23 Ep14/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Infestation Hypothesis: Amy is stuck in the middle of a battle of wills between Penny and Sheldon. Leonard and Priya try to spice up their long-distance relationship. (S5 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Pulled Groin Extrapolation: Leonard goes to a colleague's wedding as Amy's date. Howard tries to convince Bernadette to live with his mum after they get married. (S5 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Wiggly Finger Catalyst: Raj begins to get upset that he's the only one of the four guys not in a relationship, so Penny sets out to find him the perfect date. (S5 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Russian Rocket Reaction: Sheldon's old nemesis Wil Wheaton returns and invites everyone to a housewarming party. But Sheldon threatens to 'de-friend' Leonard if he attends. (S5 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Secrets of a Successful Marriage: Homer teaches a marriage guidance class but divulges a load of secrets about Marge and ends up in the doghouse. Or the tree house, at least. (S5 Ep22/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Treehouse of Horror XI: Homer receives a very scary horoscope, and Bart and Lisa are banished to the forest, where they find a house made of gingerbread... (S12 Ep1/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: E-I-E-I-(Annoyed Grunt): The Simpsons are forced to flee to the countryside, where Homer accidentally invents highly addictive tomacco. But the animals like it too... (S11 Ep5/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Marge Gamer: Marge gets hooked on an online fantasy game and discovers that Bart is the game's best - and most destructive - player. (S18 Ep17/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Celebrity Bake Off...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...for Stand Up To Cancer: Danny Dyer, Rhod Gilbert, Leigh Francis and Yinka Bokinni make mini biscuit people and a fancy tea-time classic, and recreate their biggest failure in cake form.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Mission: Impossible - Fallout
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2018) Tom Cruise stars in part six of the action-thriller series. His mission: to stop terrorists from getting their hands on nuclear bombs and unleashing global devastation.

Film4.uk.title: Inglourious Basterds
Film4.uk.description: (2009) Quentin Tarantino's World War II action-adventure. Jewish American soldiers go Nazi-hunting in occupied France. With Brad Pitt, Diane Kruger, Christoph Waltz and Michael Fassbender.

Film4.uk.title: A Private Function
Film4.uk.description: (1984) Michael Palin and Maggie Smith star in Alan Bennett's comedy set in food-rationed post-war Britain. In 1947, an illegally owned pig is secretly being fattened for a royal feast.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Hangman's Knot
Film4.uk.description: (1952) Civil War-era Western. A unit of Confederate soldiers attack a Union troop to steal gold. Learning that the war is over, they must finish the mission in disguise.

Film4.uk.title: The Winslow Boy
Film4.uk.description: (1948) Anthony Asquith's drama based on a famous 1912 court case with Cedric Hardwicke as the father of a boy accused of theft who pursues the case to the highest courts. With Robert Donat.

Film4.uk.title: Hell Is a City
Film4.uk.description: (1960) Classic crime thriller with Stanley Baker and Billie Whitelaw. A world-weary detective with a messy private life tracks a violent thief through the streets of Manchester.

Film4.uk.title: The Swimmer
Film4.uk.description: (1968) Burt Lancaster stars as the angst-ridden middle-aged man who decides to swim home via neighbour's pools in Frank and Eleanor Perry's superb allegorical drama.

Film4.uk.title: A Room with a View
Film4.uk.description: (1985) Helena Bonham Carter stars in this Merchant/Ivory film as an innocent on holiday in Florence, where a meeting with Julian Sands leads to romance.

Film4.uk.title: Transporter 3
Film4.uk.description: (2008) Violent action-thriller with Jason Statham. Terrorists hire a courier to drive a kidnapped woman across Europe, on a journey that gets ever more dangerous.

Film4.uk.title: Fury
Film4.uk.description: (2014) World War II action with Brad Pitt. A tank commander leads his crew into the dark, bloody heart of Hitler's last stand. But there's a rookie on board the Fury. With Michael Pe√±a.

Film4.uk.title: Monos
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Alejandro Landes's hallucinatory war film. A ragtag band of teenage soldiers, who live on a mountaintop in Latin America, guard an American hostage with their lives. In Spanish/subs.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Yesterday's Enemy
Film4.uk.description: (1959) Wartime drama with Stanley Baker. The captain of a British army patrol deciphers secret enemy battle plans, but does so at a great moral cost.

Film4.uk.title: Barnacle Bill
Film4.uk.description: (1957) The final Ealing comedy stars Alec Guinness as the latest in a long and distinguished line of sailors, but there's a problem: he suffers from seasickness. So why not buy a pier?

Film4.uk.title: Against the Wind
Film4.uk.description: (1948) Spy thriller. Robert Beatty, Simone Signoret, Jack Warner and Gordon Jackson star as British-trained saboteurs sent to Second World War Belgium. But one of them is a traitor...

Film4.uk.title: Nothing But the Best
Film4.uk.description: (1964) Classic British dark comedy with Alan Bates and Denholm Elliott. An ambitious estate agent's clerk hires a toff to teach him to be posh. Couldn't possibly lead to murder, could it?

Film4.uk.title: Notting Hill
Film4.uk.description: (1999) Hugh Grant and Julia Roberts star in the BAFTA-winning comedy romance about a bookshop owner who manages to get a glamorous movie star to go out with him. With Rhys Ifans.

Film4.uk.title: This Is England
Film4.uk.description: (2006) Shane Meadows' award-winning drama starring Thomas Turgoose. In the 1980s, a bullied 13-year-old finds friendship with a group of skinheads. But one of them is also a violent racist.

Film4.uk.title: Boiling Point
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Stephen Graham stars as a top chef spiralling inexorably towards destruction, as his life descends into chaos over one night's service at a fancy London restaurant.

Film4.uk.title: Memento
Film4.uk.description: (2000) Christopher Nolan's Oscar-nominated thriller with Guy Pearce. A man tracking his wife's killer has no short-term memory so must find other ways to piece together the evidence.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Mandy
Film4.uk.description: (1952) Poignant Ealing drama starring seven-year-old Mandy Miller as a deaf girl whose parents - played by Phyllis Calvert and Terence Morgan - fight over her treatment.

Film4.uk.title: The Fallen Idol
Film4.uk.description: (1948) Adaptation of Graham Greene's story with Ralph Richardson and Bobby Henrey. A butler who is accused of murdering his wife, has only a schoolboy to fight his corner.

Film4.uk.title: Nicholas Nickleby
Film4.uk.description: (1947) Drama with Derek Bond, based on Charles Dickens' novel. After his father dies, Nicholas seeks the help of his cold, avaricious, scheming uncle. Predictably, it doesn't go well.

Film4.uk.title: The Mouse That Roared
Film4.uk.description: (1959) Satirical comedy starring Peter Sellers (in a triple role) and the original Doctor Who, William Hartnell. The world's smallest state, Grand Fenwick, declares war on the USA.

Film4.uk.title: Cowboys & Aliens
Film4.uk.description: (2011) Sci-fi western starring Daniel Craig and Harrison Ford. A brutal cattle baron and his amnesiac enemy must cease their feuding when a town is attacked by aliens.

Film4.uk.title: Die Hard
Film4.uk.description: (1988) Action-thriller with Bruce Willis and Alan Rickman. Can a New York cop free the hostages being held in a skyscraper by an arch villain? Yippee ki-yay... whoops, can't say that here.

Film4.uk.title: The Drop
Film4.uk.description: (2014) Tense thriller with Tom Hardy, James Gandolfini, Noomi Rapace and Matthias Schoenaerts. Two cousins get into trouble with the gangsters who use their bar to launder illicit cash.

Film4Plus1.uk.title: Transporter 2
Film4Plus1.uk.description: (2005) Violent action-thriller starring Jason Statham as the tough courier Frank Martin, who's hired to guard a government drugs czar's son. But his mission soon lurches towards disaster.
